OL,3,CConsultants narrowly reject pay rise
OL,4,Cin latest ballot on government offer
OL,6,FHealth and Social Care Secretary
OL,7,FVictoria Atkins said: "I hugely value
OL,8,Fthe work of NHS consultants and I am
OL,9,Fdisappointed that after weeks of
OL,10,Fconstructive negotiations the BMA has,
OL,11,Fby the narrowest of margins, rejected
OL,12,Fthis fair and reasonable offer."
OL,14,FShe claims that the government hopes
OL,15,Fto improve waiting lists and focus on
OL,16,Foffering patients the highest care,
OL,17,Fand added that "the government is
OL,18,Ftherefore carefully considering next
OL,19,Fsteps."
