OL,6,F"We already know the kind of progress
OL,7,Four NHS staff can make in the absence
OL,8,Fof strikes ` waiting lists fell by
OL,9,Fmore than 95,000 in November, the
OL,10,Ffirst month without industrial action
OL,11,Ffor over a year and the biggest
OL,12,Fdecrease since December 2010 outside
OL,13,Fof the pandemic."
OL,15,FConsultants in England currently have
OL,16,Fa mandate to take strike action until
OL,17,FJune.
