OL,3,CConsultants narrowly reject pay rise
OL,4,Cin latest ballot on government offer
OL,6,FIt comes two weeks after the Hospital
OL,7,FConsultants and Specialists
OL,8,FAssociation (HCSA), which represents
OL,9,Faround 2,000 consultants, rejected an
OL,10,Foffer from the government.
OL,12,FInstead, it urged the Conservative
OL,13,Fparty to reopen negotiations after a
OL,14,F58% 'no' vote to a package the union
OL,15,Fsaid would further erode investment as
OL,16,Fwell as being "uneven" across the
OL,17,Fprofession.
