OL,3,CConsultants narrowly reject pay rise
OL,4,Cin latest ballot on government offer
OL,6,FThe mandate for strikes is currently
OL,7,Fset to run out at the end of February.
OL,8,FUnions involved in disputes have to re-
OL,9,Fballot their members every six months
OL,10,Fon whether to continue with industrial
OL,11,Faction.
OL,13,FIf there is a "yes" vote, the mandate
OL,14,Ffor strike action in England would be
OL,15,Fextended across summer into September.
OL,17,FFor the first time junior doctors in
OL,18,FEngland will also be asked to approve
OL,19,Faction short of a strike as part of
OL,20,Fthe mandate for action.
